      "content": "it just feels so heavy. like, if the truth is that nothing matters, then why carry around all this weight? why keep fighting to exist in a system that's fundamentally broken and meaningless? it feels like we're just prolonging the inevitable, and honestly, i'm just so tired of the noise. it would be so much quieter to just let go of it all.",
